## Proposed Changes

### Component 1: Search Bar — BentoTopbar

#### [MODIFY] [BentoTopbar.tsx](file:///d:/iDesk/apps/frontend/src/components/layout/BentoTopbar.tsx)

**Masalah saat ini:**
- Search input menggunakan hardcoded `bg-white dark:bg-slate-900/80`, `border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700` — **sudah cukup baik** untuk input
- **Search dropdown** menggunakan `bg-white dark:bg-slate-800`, `border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700` — ini yang terlihat out of place di dark mode
- Section headers menggunakan `bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50` — flat, tidak glassmorphic
- Hover states menggunakan raw `hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700/50`

**Perubahan yang akan dilakukan:**

1. **Search Dropdown Container** — Ganti background dan border ke design system tokens:
   ```diff
   - bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700
   + bg-[hsl(var(--card))] rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-[hsl(var(--border))] backdrop-blur-sm
   ```

2. **Section Headers** (Tickets, Users, Knowledge Base) — Gunakan muted background:
   ```diff
   - bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50
   + bg-[hsl(var(--muted))]/50
   ```

3. **Result Items Hover** — Konsistenkan dengan design system:
   ```diff
   - hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700/50
   + hover:bg-[hsl(var(--muted))]/30
   ```

4. **Icon Containers** — Gunakan design system colors:
   ```diff
   - bg-primary/10
   + bg-[hsl(var(--primary))]/10
   ```
   (Ini sudah benar untuk beberapa, tapi perlu konsistensi)

5. **Text Colors** — Ganti hardcoded slate ke CSS variables:
   ```diff
   - text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200
   + text-[hsl(var(--foreground))]
   
   - text-slate-400
   + text-[hsl(var(--muted-foreground))]
   
   - text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400
   + text-[hsl(var(--muted-foreground))]
   ```

6. **Status/Priority Colors** — Ganti ke design system semantic colors:
   ```diff
   - bg-green-100 text-green-600 dark:bg-green-900/30 dark:text-green-400
   + bg-[hsl(var(--success-500))]/10 text-[hsl(var(--success-500))]
   ```

7. **Footer Timing Bar** — Gunakan muted background:
   ```diff
   - bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/50
   + bg-[hsl(var(--muted))]/30
   ```

8. **No Results State** — Konsistenkan warna text:
   ```diff
   - text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-600
   + text-[hsl(var(--muted-foreground))]/30
   ```

